name: .VISUAL_PROCESSED File Extension
type_name: World of Tanks 3D Model Surface File
summary: Learn about .VISUAL_PROCESSED files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: 3D model surface file format used by World of Tanks (WoT), a war game featuring battles between tanks and other armored vehicles; contains texture information about the surface of a tank 3D model; replaced the .VISUAL format with the release of WoT 0.9.10.

content: You can convert WoT models to the Wavefront 3D Object format with the World of Tanks Model Converter script. The .PRIMITIVES_PROCESSED and VISUAL_PROCESSED files are required in order to create the .OBJ or .MTL file.
